{"tid":273099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應對全球暖化 ! 全球首個瑞士山區肺吸二氧化碳","createTime":"2017-06-06T10:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T15:38:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2de149f927111486a7cf7cbb820ee95f11b8fcb","tid":273099,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.price.com.hk/news.php?id=8117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.price.com.hk%2Fnews.php%3Fid%3D8117&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=73ad167d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.price.com.hk/news.php?id=8117</a><br />\n應對全球暖化 ! 全球首個「人工地球肺」工廠吸二氧化碳<br />\n23小時前 &bull; 最新情報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道森林有「地球之肺」之稱號，吸二氧化碳呼出氧氣，維持地球生態環境。不 過全球暖化加劇，而且森林漸漸少之又少，各國都努力為環保出一份力。當中瑞士一間公司 Climeworks就製造全球首間可以從大氣中吸入二氧化碳的工廠，為淨化空氣出力。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工廠設有大堆抽氣扇先抽入空氣再用過濾器收集二氧化碳，其後經加熱就可以放出純的二氧化碳。收集二氧化碳會埋在地下或者供應到需要二氧化碳的公司。當然一間工廠不可能解決 全球暖化，但這種環保概念的工廠對於人類可持續發展是相當重要。"},{"pid":"d42b18836e04697b60bf61b76aeae64eed528454","tid":273099,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170605/42c22d83ff193038f107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170605%2F42c22d83ff193038f107.jpg&h=9929d582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5a75ba7db89e68f3af26dabe1996cd3ad7f35cf","tid":273099,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/ariel0802/4bed26cdca8e9.jpg?v=1273833166\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fariel0802%2F4bed26cdca8e9.jpg%3Fv%3D1273833166&h=74b585bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9510a7f9c89317936bbeb2ed8f1eaeaa777e8e0e","tid":273099,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾勁"},{"pid":"75e3cbb6ec20121a8f28ec1491a9838341f1c429","tid":273099,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"抽嘅過程，用電唔會產生二氧化碳？<br />\n賣完二氧化碳俾其他公司用完啲二氧化碳都係係返地球度姐🤔又唔係變返氧氣<br />\n咁咪仲產多左二氧化碳？"},{"pid":"841be89a4fc449b7b735d05d29b62d7eb866b133","tid":273099,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽嘅過程，用電唔會產生二氧化碳？<br />\n賣完二氧化碳俾其他公司用完啲二氧化碳都係係返地球度姐🤔又唔係變返氧氣<br />\n咁咪仲產多左二氧化碳？</blockquote><br />\n太陽能"},{"pid":"98a932deba2013c5f440043b7809dcbd6b4873c3","tid":273099,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解決全球暖化其實好簡單，用核彈炸撚左巴拿馬/中美洲個堆國家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整斷墨西哥暖流，寫包單北極冰一定融少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再想玩大d，可以同時間用氫彈狂炸活火山，逼多d火山灰出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或姐瘋狂係北非無人沙漠瘋狂核試，炸哂d沙出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebac84ae1af2d102212b95b04db6b1b856869f1","tid":273099,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60ea9b0a43fba69d75f373b85ca9ae2b76a672","tid":273099,"uid":27362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/182453_650a485798b75e14d3937a63db988a4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F182453_650a485798b75e14d3937a63db988a4c.jpg&h=8153ccc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cba0a44f6ebc82fe4c3182